Integrate Firebase:
    Log-in into firebase.com
    Create a new project
    Set its nickname

    In it's authentication portion, copy the config portion and paste it in your firebase.js

Commands for deploying/hosting your webapp in firebase:
IN CLI:
    $ firebase login     (if you aren't logged in already )
    $ firebase init
        CHOOSE: Hosting: Configure and deploy Firebase Hosting sites (using space and then enter)
        ? Please select an option: Use an existing project
        ? Select a default Firebase project for this directory: clone-769e2 (amazon-clone)
        ? What do you want to use as your public directory? build
        ? Configure as a single-page app (rewrite all urls to/index.html)? Yes
    $ firebase deploy